<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3699869>
    dc:description "FIG. 10. — Pachynolophus sp. from Aumelas: A, AUM 199, right maxillary fragment with P3/-M3/; A1, labial view; A2, occlusal view; B, AUM 1586, right maxillary fragment with (alv. P1/)-P2/-(M2/); B1, labial view; B2, occlusal view; C, AUM 213, left M3/ (reversed), occlusal view; D, AUM 1596, left fragment with P3/-P4/ (reversed),occlusal view;E, AUM 332, right DP/4,occlusal view;F, AUM 1600,right mandible with M/2-M/3 (pars); F1, occlusal view;F2, labial view;G, AUM 323, symphysis with both /C and sockets of incisors, dorsal view; H, AUM 1599 left mandible fragment with (P/3)-(M/3) (reversed); H1, occlusal view; H2, labial view; I, AUM 1620, left mandible with DP/2-M/2-(M/3), occlusal view; J, AUM 1617, mandible with right /C-(alv. DP/1)-DP/2-M/3, sockets of incisors and left /C); J1, occlusal view; J2, labial view. Scale bars: 2 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3699869/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

